\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Z\u225\'e1kon utv\u225\'e1ra legislat\u237\'edvne podmienky na z\u225\'e1sadn\u233\'e9 zmeny v syst\u233\'e9me odme\u328\'48ovania pedagogick\u253\'fdch zamestnancov a odborn\u253\'fdch zamestnancov v nadv\u228\'e4znosti na kontinu\u225\'e1lne vzdel\u225\'e1vanie t\u253\'fdchto skup\u237\'edn, ktor\u233\'e9 sa uplatnia aj v novelizovanom z\u225\'e1kone \u269\'0d. 553 o odme\u328\'48ovan\u237\'ed niektor\u253\'fdch zamestnancov pri v\u253\'fdkone pr\u225\'e1ce vo verejnom z\u225\'e1ujme. T\u225\'e1to \u269\'0das\u357\'65 je predkladan\u225\'e1 v tomto n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona ako \u269\'0dl. 3. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
