\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pova\u382\'7eujem za potrebn\u233\'e9 zd\u244\'f4razni\u357\'65 aj to, \u382\'7ee z\u225\'e1kon je nastaven\u253\'fd ako motiva\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd n\u225\'e1stroj pre zvy\u353\'61ovanie  profesijn\u253\'fdch kompetenci\u237\'ed. Pedagogick\u253\'fd alebo odborn\u253\'fd zamestnanec si m\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee vybra\u357\'65 z dvoch kari\u233\'e9rov\u253\'fdch ciest. Prvou cestou je horizont\u225\'e1lny rast, a to udr\u382\'7eiavanie si pr\u237\'edslu\u353\'61n\u253\'fdch profesijn\u253\'fdch kompetenci\u237\'ed pre pr\u237\'edslu\u353\'61n\u253\'fd kari\u233\'e9rov\u253\'fd stupe\u328\'48 prostredn\u237\'edctvom vzdel\u225\'e1vania, za ktor\u233\'e9 si z\u237\'edskava kredity a n\u225\'e1sledne kreditov\u253\'fd pr\u237\'edplatok. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
