\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Rovnako z\u225\'e1kon upravuje starostlivos\u357\'65 o pedagogick\u233\'e9ho zamestnanca a odborn\u233\'e9ho zamestnanca v oblasti zdravotnej starostlivosti a regener\u225\'e1cie pracovnej sily, soci\u225\'e1lnej starostlivosti, prevencie pred n\u225\'e1rastom agresie a n\u225\'e1silia a mor\u225\'e1lneho oce\u328\'48ovania. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V zmysle uveden\u233\'e9ho je cie\u318\'3eom z\u225\'e1kona komplexn\u233\'e9 rie\u353\'61enie postavenia, profesijn\u233\'e9ho rozvoja a kari\u233\'e9rov\u233\'e9ho rastu pedagogick\u253\'fdch zamestnancov a odborn\u253\'fdch zamestnancov \u353\'61k\u244\'f4l, \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fdch zariaden\u237\'ed a ostatn\u253\'fdch zariaden\u237\'ed, v ktor\u253\'fdch sa vykon\u225\'e1va v\u253\'fdchova a vzdel\u225\'e1vanie aj v p\u244\'f4sobnosti in\u253\'fdch \u250\'fastredn\u253\'fdch org\u225\'e1nov \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnej spr\u225\'e1vy a taktie\u382\'7e pedagogick\u253\'fdch zamestnancov v zariadeniach pre kontinu\u225\'e1lne vzdel\u225\'e1vanie pedagogick\u253\'fdch zamestnancov. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
