T. Cabaj, podpredseda NR SR: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eakujem pekne. S faktickou pozn\u225\'e1mkou nikto nechce reagova\u357\'65? S faktickou pozn\u225\'e1mkou chce reagova\u357\'65 p\u225\'e1n Fronc. Kon\u269\'0d\u237\'edm mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 prihl\u225\'e1si\u357\'65 sa s faktickou pozn\u225\'e1mkou. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Nech sa p\u225\'e1\u269\'0di, p\u225\'e1n poslanec, m\u225\'e1te slovo.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\afs30\ab\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
M. Fronc, poslanec: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eakujem pekne, p\u225\'e1n predsedaj\u250\'faci. Pani kolegy\u328\'48a povedala \u271\'0fal\u353\'61ie v\u253\'fdhrady k n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona. Mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee v\u225\'e1\u382\'7ene v\u253\'fdhrady. Niektor\u233\'e9 sa opakovali s t\u253\'fdmi v\u253\'fdhradami, ktor\u233\'e9 som povedal ja, tak by som chcel po\u382\'7eiada\u357\'65 p\u225\'e1na ministra, aby reagoval a nereagoval potom len v z\u225\'e1vere\u269\'0dnom slove, aby aspo\u328\'48 tak\u253\'fdmto sp\u244\'f4sobom mohlo d\u244\'f4js\u357\'65 k takej, by som povedal, malej n\u225\'e1hrade rokovania vo v\u253\'fdbore, ktor\u233\'e9 neprebehlo tak, ako malo prebehn\u250\'fa\u357\'65. \u270\'0eakujem.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6

