I. Andrusk\u243\'f3, poslanec: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eakujem pekne za slovo. V\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n podpredseda, mil\u233\'e9 kolegyne, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u237\'ed kolegovia, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n podpredseda vl\u225\'e1dy, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n minister, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u225\'e1 pani spravodajky\u328\'48a, znova sa stret\u225\'e1vame s my\u353\'61lienkami, ktor\u233\'e9 sprev\u225\'e1dzali rozpravu o n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona o pedagogick\u253\'fdch pracovn\u237\'edkoch v N\u225\'e1rodnej rade pred nieko\u318\'3ek\u253\'fdmi t\u253\'fd\u382\'7ed\u328\'48ami. S po\u318\'3eutovan\u237\'edm v\u353\'61ak mus\u237\'edm kon\u353\'61tatova\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee odvtedy \u382\'7eiadny probl\u233\'e9m nebol rie\u353\'61en\u253\'fd, ani \u382\'7eiadna inovat\u237\'edvna, respekt\u237\'edve zlep\u353\'61uj\u250\'faca my\u353\'61lienka zatia\u318\'3e nebola akceptovan\u225\'e1. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V\u353\'61etci vieme, \u382\'7ee pedagogick\u225\'e1 obec ve\u318\'3emi o\u269\'0dak\u225\'e1va tento z\u225\'e1kon. U\u269\'0ditelia prostredn\u237\'edctvom svojich odborov\u253\'fdch organiz\u225\'e1ci\u237\'ed toti\u382\'7e u\u382\'7e nieko\u318\'3ekokr\u225\'e1t vyjadrili z\u225\'e1ujem o korektn\u233\'e9 rie\u353\'61enie svojho spolo\u269\'0densk\u233\'e9ho postavenia. Ned\u225\'e1vno som v\u225\'e1m u\u382\'7e spom\u237\'ednal, \u382\'7ee aj ja pracujem v pedagogickom kolekt\u237\'edve a m\u225\'e1m mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 z bezprostrednej bl\u237\'edzkosti sledova\u357\'65 \u382\'7eivot u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov. Ve\u318\'3emi dobre viem, \u382\'7ee neo\u269\'0dak\u225\'e1vaj\u250\'fa \u382\'7eiadne jednostrann\u233\'e9 gest\u225\'e1. V pr\u237\'edpade potreby toti\u382\'7e s\u250\'fa ochotn\u237\'ed aj oni polo\u382\'7ei\u357\'65 viac na spolo\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd st\u244\'f4l. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ak nov\u233\'e9 normy zlep\u353\'61ia spolo\u269\'0densk\u233\'e9 postavenie u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov, od v\u228\'e4\u269\'0d\u353\'61iny pedag\u243\'f3gov skuto\u269\'0dne m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eeme o\u269\'0dak\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 \u271\'0fal\u353\'61iu pridan\u250\'fa hodnotu vo svojej pr\u225\'e1ci. Nako\u318\'3eko v\u353\'61ak zo strany z\u225\'e1konotvorcov neboli akceptovan\u233\'e9 \u382\'7eiadne zlep\u353\'61ovacie n\u225\'e1vrhy, mus\u237\'edm v\u225\'e1s znovu upozorni\u357\'65 na niektor\u233\'e9 skryt\u233\'e9 probl\u233\'e9my, ktor\u233\'e9 po schv\u225\'e1len\u237\'ed z\u225\'e1kona v s\u250\'fa\u269\'0dasnej podobe m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eu ma\u357\'65 aj z\u225\'e1porn\u253\'fd dopad na celkov\u250\'fa situ\u225\'e1ciu v pedagogick\u253\'fdch kolekt\u237\'edvoch. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
N\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona neobsahuje \u382\'7eiadne garancie ani na krytie finan\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdch n\u225\'e1kladov s\u250\'favisiacich so zv\u253\'fd\u353\'61en\u237\'edm kvalifik\u225\'e1cie pedagogick\u253\'fdch zamestnancov. Neobsahuje mienku o valoriz\u225\'e1cii platov ani o finan\u269\'0dnom kryt\u237\'ed bodov, takzvan\u253\'fdch kreditov z\u237\'edskan\u253\'fdch v procese kontinu\u225\'e1lneho vzdel\u225\'e1vania u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V\u353\'61etci vieme, \u382\'7ee svetov\u225\'e1 hospod\u225\'e1rska kr\u237\'edza m\u225\'e1 svoj dopad aj na slovensk\u250\'fa. Pr\u225\'e1ve preto vhodn\u225\'e1 garancia na krytie t\u253\'fdchto n\u225\'e1kladov by bola nevyhnutn\u225\'e1  nielen z d\u244\'f4vodu uspokojenia verejnej mienky, ale aj z d\u244\'f4vodu zachovania v\u225\'e1\u382\'7enosti tohto n\u225\'e1vrhu. V s\u250\'fa\u269\'0dasn\u253\'fdch podmienkach tak\u250\'fato garanciu pr\u225\'e1vom o\u269\'0dak\u225\'e1va nielen pedagogick\u225\'e1 obec, ale cel\u225\'e1 spolo\u269\'0dnos\u357\'65. Ak v m\u225\'e1ji 2009 je schodok \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tneho rozpo\u269\'0dtu v miliard\u225\'e1ch eur, ani ja, ani nikto in\u253\'fd nem\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee vidie\u357\'65 re\u225\'e1lne krytie nav\u253\'fd\u353\'61enia objemu pr\u225\'e1ce a\~u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov, respekt\u237\'edve zv\u253\'fd\u353\'61enie kvality pr\u225\'e1ce. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Nov\u253\'fd syst\u233\'e9m chce rie\u353\'61i\u357\'65 ot\u225\'e1zku zlep\u353\'61enia finan\u269\'0dnej situ\u225\'e1cie u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov. Pre niektor\u253\'fdch riadite\u318\'3eov \u353\'61k\u244\'f4l a \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fdch zariaden\u237\'ed v\u353\'61ak m\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee znamena\u357\'65 \u357\'65a\u382\'7eko rie\u353\'61ite\u318\'3en\u253\'fd probl\u233\'e9m. Nako\u318\'3eko v z\u225\'e1ujme zlep\u353\'61enia vlastnej situ\u225\'e1cie na r\u244\'f4zne formy kontinu\u225\'e1lneho vzdel\u225\'e1vania sa bude hl\u225\'e1si\u357\'65 relat\u237\'edvne ve\u318\'3ek\u253\'fd po\u269\'0det u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov, v niektor\u253\'fdch vyu\u269\'0dovac\u237\'edch d\u328\'48och bude na \u353\'61kol\u225\'e1ch nedostato\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd po\u269\'0det u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ak riadite\u318\'3e po istom \u269\'0dase za\u269\'0dne selektova\u357\'65, koho pust\u237\'ed a koho nepust\u237\'ed na \u353\'61kolenia, m\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee to ma\u357\'65 za n\u225\'e1sledok aj osobn\u233\'e9 konflikty na \u353\'61kol\u225\'e1ch. Syst\u233\'e9m by naplnil svoje poslanie len vtedy, ak by podujatia v r\u225\'e1mci kontinu\u225\'e1lneho vzdel\u225\'e1vania boli organizovan\u233\'e9 v\u253\'fdlu\u269\'0dne mimo vyu\u269\'0dovacieho \u269\'0dasu, \u269\'0do je, samozrejme, nere\u225\'e1lne. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Preto osobne pova\u382\'7eujem za nevyhnutn\u233\'e9 na \u250\'farovni ni\u382\'7e\u353\'61\u237\'edch pr\u225\'e1vnych noriem o\u353\'61etri\u357\'65 aj t\u250\'fato ot\u225\'e1zku a pred\u237\'eds\u357\'65 situ\u225\'e1ci\u225\'e1m, ktor\u233\'e9 by rozde\u318\'3eovali doteraz kompaktn\u233\'e9 pedagogick\u233\'e9 kolekt\u237\'edvy.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
N\u225\'e1vrh sa nezaober\u225\'e1 dostato\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdm sp\u244\'f4sobom ani s pr\u237\'edpadom u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov, ktor\u237\'ed svoje kvality u\u382\'7e nieko\u318\'3eko rokov dokazuj\u250\'fa permanentn\u253\'fdmi vynikaj\u250\'facimi v\u253\'fdsledkami napr\u237\'edklad na predmetov\u253\'fdch olympi\u225\'e1dach. Pre\u269\'0do tak\u253\'fdto pedag\u243\'f3g nem\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee svojimi v\u253\'fdsledkami z\u237\'edska\u357\'65 tak\u253\'fd po\u269\'0det bodov kreditov, ktor\u253\'fd by bol adekv\u225\'e1tny jeho pr\u225\'e1ci, respekt\u237\'edve sa vyrovn\u225\'e1 po\u269\'0dtu bodov z\u237\'edskan\u253\'fdch r\u244\'f4znymi \u353\'61koleniami za \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fd rok. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ak napr\u237\'edklad v niektorom \u353\'61kolskom roku a\u382\'7e dvaja \u382\'7eiaci u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3ea reprezentuj\u250\'fa Slovensk\u250\'fa republiku na medzin\u225\'e1rodnej predmetovej olympi\u225\'e1de, mal som tak\u253\'fd pr\u237\'edklad napr\u237\'edklad na \u353\'61kole, pre\u269\'0do t\u225\'e1to skuto\u269\'0dnos\u357\'65 nesta\u269\'0d\u237\'ed za plnohodnotn\u250\'fa n\u225\'e1hradu v\u353\'61etk\u253\'fdch mo\u382\'7en\u253\'fdch bodov, kreditov z\u237\'edskan\u253\'fdch za \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fd rok na r\u244\'f4znych \u353\'61koleniach. Je tam asi 20 kreditov, tak ten pedag\u243\'f3g by z\u237\'edskal 20 kreditov. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Tvrdohlav\u253\'fd odpor proti uzn\u225\'e1vania hodn\u244\'f4t \u353\'61pi\u269\'0dkov\u253\'fdch u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov sved\u269\'0d\u237\'ed len o tom, \u382\'7ee tvorcovia z\u225\'e1kona aj v tomto pr\u237\'edpade sleduj\u250\'fa len sebeck\u233\'e9 ciele, a to zabezpe\u269\'0denie dobr\u233\'e9ho a permanentn\u233\'e9ho biznisu pre svojich zn\u225\'e1mych a pr\u237\'edbuzn\u253\'fdch, ktor\u237\'ed pracuj\u250\'fa alebo bud\u250\'fa pracova\u357\'65 v in\u353\'61tit\u250\'faci\u225\'e1ch zabezpe\u269\'0duj\u250\'facich kontinu\u225\'e1lne vzdel\u225\'e1vanie. Ve\u271\'0f sa o tom m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eeme onedlho presved\u269\'0di\u357\'65, ale vtedy u\u382\'7e bude neskoro. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Zo znenia n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona nevypl\u253\'fdva jednozna\u269\'0dne ani pou\u382\'7eitie kreditn\u253\'fdch bodov z\u237\'edskan\u253\'fdch v procese kontinu\u225\'e1lneho vzdel\u225\'e1vania. Ak toti\u382\'7e pedag\u243\'f3g za ist\u253\'fd po\u269\'0det rokov pozbiera potrebn\u253\'fd po\u269\'0det bodov, nie je jednozna\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9, \u269\'0di v\u353\'61etky jeho body zostan\u250\'fa platn\u233\'e9 za sedem rokov, alebo v ka\u382\'7edom roku strat\u237\'ed zo svojich bodov tie, ktor\u233\'e9 boli z\u237\'edskan\u233\'e9 pred \u244\'f4smimi rokmi napr\u237\'edklad. Ak toti\u382\'7e napr\u237\'edklad pred \u244\'f4smimi rokmi z\u237\'edskal na \u353\'61koleniach nadpriemern\u253\'fd po\u269\'0det bodov pri takomto \u353\'61t\u253\'fdle z\u237\'edskan\u253\'fdm ro\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9ho priemern\u233\'e9ho po\u269\'0dtu bodov nem\u225\'e1 mo\u382\'7enos\u357\'65 znova dobehn\u250\'fa\u357\'65 potrebn\u253\'fd po\u269\'0det bodov, kreditov na postup do \u271\'0fal\u353\'61ej kateg\u243\'f3rie. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Paralelne s t\u253\'fdm ve\u318\'3ek\u253\'fd po\u269\'0det odborn\u253\'fdch pr\u225\'e1c \u8211\'13 p\u228\'e4\u357\'65 a\u382\'7e \u353\'61es\u357\'65 potrebn\u253\'fdch na dosiahnutie 60 bodov pripom\u237\'edna sk\u244\'f4r \u353\'61ikanovanie u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov a nie syst\u233\'e9m, ktor\u253\'fd sl\u250\'fa\u382\'7ei na ich motiv\u225\'e1ciu a \u271\'0fal\u353\'61ie vzdel\u225\'e1vanie. Pr\u225\'e1ve preto pros\u237\'edm v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fdch pr\u237\'edtomn\u253\'fdch, aby sa sna\u382\'7eili premiestni\u357\'65 tento probl\u233\'e9m. V opa\u269\'0dnom pr\u237\'edpade toti\u382\'7e budeme svedkami aj tak\u253\'fdch pr\u237\'edpadov, ke\u271\'0f sa syst\u233\'e9m zmen\u237\'ed na bezo\u269\'0div\u250\'fa a nekal\u250\'fa s\u250\'fa\u357\'65a\u382\'7e u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov pri zabezpe\u269\'0dovan\u237\'ed svojej \u250\'fa\u269\'0dasti na podujatiach kontinu\u225\'e1lneho vzdel\u225\'e1vania. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
A na z\u225\'e1ver, ako to povedal predt\u253\'fdm p\u225\'e1n podpredseda v\u253\'fdboru L\u225\'e1szl\u243\'f3 Szigeti, tento z\u225\'e1kon potrebujeme a nie v takejto podobe. \u270\'0eakujem pekne za pozornos\u357\'65.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\afs30\ab\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
T. Cabaj, podpredseda NR SR: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eakujem pekne. Na vyst\u250\'fapenie ako posledn\u253\'fd p\u237\'edsomne prihl\u225\'e1sen\u253\'fd je aj p\u225\'e1n poslanec Jaroslav Ivan\u269\'0do. Nech sa p\u225\'e1\u269\'0di, m\u225\'e1te slovo.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6

\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\b\afs30\ab\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
J. Ivan\u269\'0do, poslanec: }{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
V\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n podpredseda, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u253\'fd p\u225\'e1n minister, pani spravodajky\u328\'48a, mil\u233\'e9 d\u225\'e1my, v\u225\'e1\u382\'7een\u237\'ed p\u225\'e1ni, m\u225\'e1m priate\u318\'3ea, ktor\u253\'fd sa venuje atletike a ten vie, \u269\'0do znamen\u225\'e1, ke\u271\'0f je zvonenie do posledn\u233\'e9ho kola. Tak\u382\'7ee zvonenie do posledn\u233\'e9ho kola v pr\u237\'edprave z\u225\'e1kona, pr\u237\'edprave pr\u225\'e1vnej normy, ktor\u225\'e1 by mala upravova\u357\'65 postavenie u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov, mala by definova\u357\'65 kvalitu u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eskej profesie a spolo\u269\'0densk\u253\'fd status. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Cesty, ktor\u233\'e9 ved\u250\'fa k pochopeniu tohto cie\u318\'3ea, s\u250\'fa iste mnoh\u233\'e9. Ministerstvo \u353\'61kolstva si vybralo pod\u318\'3ea m\u328\'48a ve\u318\'3emi n\u225\'e1ro\u269\'0dn\u250\'fa cestu pr\u237\'edpravy takejto normy a treba poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee po mnoh\u253\'fdch rokoch je dobr\u233\'e9, \u382\'7ee m\u225\'e1me na stole ucelen\u253\'fd n\u225\'e1vrh pr\u225\'e1vnej normy, ktor\u225\'e1 sa venuje povolaniu u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3ea. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pochopenie u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eskej profesie, pochopenie kvality tejto profesie, ako som uviedol spolo\u269\'0densk\u233\'e9ho statusu v predlo\u382\'7eenej norme znamen\u225\'e1 vlastne vytvorenie syst\u233\'e9mu vzdel\u225\'e1vania, syst\u233\'e9mu kari\u233\'e9rneho rastu, ale aj syst\u233\'e9mu odme\u328\'48ovania. Sp\u244\'f4sob, ak\u253\'fdm to chceme dosiahnu\u357\'65, efekt, ktor\u253\'fd si \u382\'7eel\u225\'e1me, je v\u353\'61ak, ako som povedal, diskutabiln\u253\'fd. Pre\u269\'0do? }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Za jeden zo z\u225\'e1kladn\u253\'fdch determinantov zmien v slovenskom vzdel\u225\'e1vacom syst\u233\'e9me a nielen pri tomto z\u225\'e1kone, ale aj pri \u353\'61kolskom z\u225\'e1kone sme pokladali, alebo sa hovorilo aj \u353\'61t\u250\'fadie dok\u225\'e1zali, \u382\'7ee jeden z t\u253\'fdchto z\u225\'e1kladn\u253\'fdch determinantov je to, \u382\'7ee pre\u269\'0do nem\u225\'e1me tak\u233\'e9 \u353\'61kolstvo, ako by sme si \u382\'7eelali, ako by si \u382\'7eelala spolo\u269\'0dnos\u357\'65, je to, \u382\'7ee vzdel\u225\'e1vac\u237\'ed syst\u233\'e9m je pr\u237\'edli\u353\'61 uzavret\u253\'fd. U\u269\'0dite\u318\'3esk\u225\'e1 profesia je pr\u237\'edli\u353\'61 uzavret\u225\'e1 do seba a ch\u253\'fdba ist\u253\'fd stupe\u328\'48 otvorenosti vo\u269\'0di spolo\u269\'0dnosti ako takej. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee bola \u353\'61anca v tejto norme, v tomto n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona viac otvori\u357\'65 vzdel\u225\'e1vac\u237\'ed syst\u233\'e9m, tak ako si to mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee to bolo pri \u353\'61kolskom z\u225\'e1kone nezodpovednos\u357\'65ou p\u225\'e1na ministra ako predkladate\u318\'3ea, ako to pripravil. M\u244\'f4j osobn\u253\'fd n\u225\'e1zor je, \u382\'7ee ur\u269\'0dite sa tam dali vytvori\u357\'65 nov\u233\'e9 pr\u237\'edstupy. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ak p\u244\'f4jdeme do obsahu z\u225\'e1kona, tak pritom vznikaj\u250\'fa ot\u225\'e1zky, \u382\'7ee ak chceme u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov vzdel\u225\'e1va\u357\'65, ale nechceme, aby ich vzdel\u225\'e1vali in\u233\'e9 organiz\u225\'e1cie ako tie, ktor\u233\'e9 v podstate priamo zria\u271\'0fuje ministerstvo \u353\'61kolstva, tak potom na \u269\'0do m\u225\'e1me in\u353\'61tit\u250\'faciu alebo in\u353\'61tit\u250\'fat akredita\u269\'0dnej rady, ktor\u250\'fa zria\u271\'0fujeme ako poradn\u253\'fd org\u225\'e1n a pri tom v sp\u228\'e4tnej v\u228\'e4zbe si treba uvedomi\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee t\u225\'e1to akredita\u269\'0dn\u225\'e1 rada v podstate bude vyd\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 poradn\u233\'e9 stanovisko k akredit\u225\'e1cii vzdel\u225\'e1vac\u237\'edch programov kontinu\u225\'e1lneho vzdel\u225\'e1vania, ale k akredit\u225\'e1cii t\u253\'fdch programov vzdel\u225\'e1vania, ktor\u233\'e9 pripravia  organiz\u225\'e1cie ministerstva \u353\'61kolstva v\~podstate \u8211\'13 metodicko-pedagogick\u233\'e9 centrum, \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tny \u250\'fastav odborn\u233\'e9ho vzdel\u225\'e1vania a podobne. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee je to tro\u353\'61ku \u250\'faplne zbyto\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9, preto\u382\'7ee ministerstvo \u353\'61kolstva, ak m\u225\'e1 ist\u250\'fa hierarchiu riadenia, tak vie zabezpe\u269\'0di\u357\'65 v t\u253\'fdchto organiz\u225\'e1ci\u225\'e1ch aj to, aby sa tam pripravili tak\u233\'e9 programy kontinu\u225\'e1lneho vzdel\u225\'e1vania, ktor\u233\'e9 by boli v s\u250\'falade so smerovan\u237\'edm a s politikou ministerstva.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pri podobnom \u353\'61t\u250\'fadiu n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona vlastne zist\u237\'edme, \u382\'7ee podstatou tohto n\u225\'e1vrhu je to, aby sa u\u269\'0ditelia u\u269\'0dili, a ke\u271\'0f sa bud\u250\'fa dobre u\u269\'0di\u357\'65, za to dostan\u250\'fa aj ist\u233\'e9 peniaze. A to som r\u225\'e1d, \u382\'7ee sa to takto pon\u237\'edma, lebo toto skuto\u269\'0dne aj treba. Ale ako som povedal, hor\u353\'61ie na tom je to, \u382\'7ee sa t\u237\'ed u\u269\'0ditelia aj doteraz u\u269\'0dili, len nemali peniaze a po novom sa bud\u250\'fa u\u269\'0di\u357\'65 takisto a v t\u253\'fdch ist\u253\'fdch organiz\u225\'e1ci\u225\'e1ch, ako sa u\u269\'0dili doteraz, a pritom im nechceme uzna\u357\'65 to doteraj\u353\'61ie vzdel\u225\'e1vanie, len teda po roku 2005. M\u225\'e1m pocit, \u382\'7ee tu chceme vytvori\u357\'65 nie\u269\'0do, \u269\'0do vlastne u\u382\'7e funguje, len to nebolo dotiahnut\u233\'e9 na vy\u353\'61\u353\'61iu \u250\'farove\u328\'48. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Zost\u225\'e1va teda ot\u225\'e1zkou, \u382\'7ee ke\u271\'0f sa doteraz vyu\u382\'7e\u237\'edvali mo\u382\'7enosti vzdel\u225\'e1vania u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov v priamo riaden\u253\'fdch organiz\u225\'e1ci\u225\'e1ch a nez\u237\'edskavali sa len kredity, \u269\'0di by nebolo mo\u382\'7en\u233\'e9 potom pod\u318\'3ea filozofie predlo\u382\'7eenej normy pripravi\u357\'65 len n\u225\'e1vrh o kreditnom alebo kari\u233\'e9rnom raste, alebo kreditnom syst\u233\'e9me. A\u382\'7e v tejto s\u250\'favislosti ma oslovil jeden kolega, \u269\'0di by nebolo dobr\u233\'e9, keby u\u269\'0ditelia namiesto kreditov dost\u225\'e1vali kreditky rovno. Mo\u382\'7eno, \u382\'7ee by to tie\u382\'7e pomohlo. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ak si doplnia u\u269\'0ditelia vzdelanie, tak post\u250\'fapia na z\u225\'e1klade kreditov platovo vy\u353\'61\u353\'61ie a\u382\'7e o nejak\u253\'fdch mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee 12 % m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eu za nieko\u318\'3eko desiatok kreditov. \u268\'0co je v\u353\'61ak \u269\'0darovn\u233\'e9, \u382\'7ee ak dosiahnu vrchol v kontinu\u225\'e1lnom vzdel\u225\'e1van\u237\'ed v pr\u237\'edslu\u353\'61nej platovej triede a urobia si okrem toho e\u353\'61te vzdel\u225\'e1vanie, ktor\u233\'e9 ich posunie do inej platovej triedy, vr\u225\'e1tia sa nasp\u228\'e4\u357\'65. Bud\u250\'fa s\u237\'edce vo vy\u353\'61\u353\'61ej platovej triede, ale op\u228\'e4\u357\'65 nechcem poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee \u353\'61tartuj\u250\'fa na nule, lebo bud\u250\'fa ma\u357\'65 nie o 12 % vy\u353\'61\u353\'61\u237\'ed plat, ako ke\u271\'0f kon\u269\'0dili v platovej triede, ale vr\u225\'e1tia sa na \u250\'farove\u328\'48 len o 5 % vy\u353\'61\u353\'61\u237\'ed plat a zase sa m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eu vzdel\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 a\~z\u237\'edskava\u357\'65, ako ministrovi sa mu to nep\u225\'e1\u269\'0di, kreditky, ale kredity. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Nemysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee to je celkom syst\u233\'e9m spravodliv\u253\'fd a\~to, \u269\'0do sme chceli dosiahnu\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee je to aj syst\u233\'e9m motiva\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd a navrhnem, aby v spolo\u269\'0dnej spr\u225\'e1ve bolo osobitn\u233\'e9 hlasovanie o tomto bode, ja to e\u353\'61te poviem na z\u225\'e1ver tie body presne, o tomto bode, aby sa jednoducho o\u269\'0distilo od tak\u253\'fdchto nedokonalost\u237\'ed tento n\u225\'e1vrh.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Probl\u233\'e9mom je to, \u382\'7ee vzdel\u225\'e1vanie, ako som uviedol, nebude otvoren\u233\'e9, lebo nep\u250\'fa\u353\'61\u357\'65ame do priestorov nov\u253\'fdch poskytovate\u318\'3eov. Ak chcem pripusti\u357\'65 ist\u250\'fa mieru pokory opoz\u237\'edcie, tak si viem predstavi\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee priamo riaden\u233\'e9 organiz\u225\'e1cie bud\u250\'fa vzdel\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov vo funk\u269\'0dnom vzdel\u225\'e1van\u237\'ed. Tam chceme, aby si ten \u353\'61t\u225\'e1t udr\u382\'7eiaval ist\u250\'fa svoju filozofiu. Ale absol\u250\'fatne je pre m\u328\'48a neprijate\u318\'3en\u233\'e9, aby do syst\u233\'e9mu nevst\u250\'fapili in\u237\'ed poskytovatelia napr\u237\'edklad pri inova\u269\'0dnom alebo \u353\'61pecializa\u269\'0dnom vzdel\u225\'e1van\u237\'ed, preto\u382\'7ee pr\u225\'e1ve inov\u225\'e1cie s\u250\'fa t\u253\'fdm prvkom, kde nielen \u353\'61t\u225\'e1t prin\u225\'e1\u353\'61a nov\u233\'e9 podmienky, a to hovor\u237\'edm z\u225\'e1merne nielen, lebo aj \u353\'61t\u225\'e1t, ale mnoh\u233\'e9 in\u233\'e9 ob\u269\'0dianske zdru\u382\'7eenia, in\u237\'ed poskytovatelia by mohli prinies\u357\'65 nov\u253\'fd vietor do inova\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9ho vzdel\u225\'e1vania.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Preto v mojom pozme\u328\'48uj\u250\'facom n\u225\'e1vrhu navrhnem zmenu, ktor\u225\'e1 sa bude t\u253\'fdka\u357\'65 pr\u225\'e1ve toho, aby, a to chcem zd\u244\'f4razni\u357\'65, v inova\u269\'0dnom a \u353\'61pecializa\u269\'0dnom vzdel\u225\'e1van\u237\'ed mohli vystupova\u357\'65 aj in\u237\'ed poskytovatelia pr\u225\'e1ve na z\u225\'e1klade toho, \u382\'7ee akredita\u269\'0dn\u225\'e1 rada, ktor\u250\'fa zria\u271\'0fuje ministerstvo, by tieto programy akreditovala, \u269\'0do si mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee by aj bolo v podstate naplnenie jej skuto\u269\'0dnej podstaty existencie. My to, \u269\'0do m\u225\'e1me vzdel\u225\'e1vanie, tak m\u225\'e1me teraz a budeme ma\u357\'65 vlastne aj po novom. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pr\u225\'e1ve reformn\u233\'e9 pohyby v eur\u243\'f3pskych krajin\u225\'e1ch sa pos\u250\'favaj\u250\'fa tou cestou, \u382\'7ee p\u250\'fa\u353\'61\u357\'65aj\u250\'fa do syst\u233\'e9mu vzdel\u225\'e1vania u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov pr\u225\'e1ve \u353\'61ir\u353\'61ie pole in\u253\'fdch poskytovate\u318\'3eov a s\u250\'fa v snahe o diverzifik\u225\'e1ciu vzdel\u225\'e1vac\u237\'edch ciest, o cel\u250\'fa flexibilitu cel\u233\'e9ho vzdel\u225\'e1vania u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov. V tomto n\u225\'e1vrhu, ak ho pon\u237\'edmame kriticky, m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eeme poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee financovanie vzdel\u225\'e1vania sa v podstate pren\u225\'e1\u353\'61a na \u353\'61koly a na samospr\u225\'e1vy, \u269\'0do si nemysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee je celkom spr\u225\'e1vne. Zo strany \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tu je tento n\u225\'e1vrh v celej u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eskej profesii v kontexte prij\u237\'edman\u253\'fdch z\u225\'e1konov touto soci\u225\'e1lnou vl\u225\'e1dou maco\u353\'61sk\u253\'fd. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Na tejto sch\u244\'f4dzi sme prerokovali n\u225\'e1vrhy, ktor\u233\'e9 v\u253\'fdrazne zlep\u353\'61uj\u250\'fa postavenie divadeln\u253\'fdch zamestnancov, p\u225\'e1na poslanca Jarjabka tam vid\u237\'edm. Po\u269\'0das minulej sch\u244\'f4dze sme prij\u237\'edmali z\u225\'e1kony, ktor\u233\'e9 v\u253\'fdrazne zlep\u353\'61uj\u250\'fa postavenie ban\u237\'edkov. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Na tejto sch\u244\'f4dzi sme prerokovali n\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona, ktor\u253\'fd v\u253\'fdrazne zlep\u353\'61uje, a to chcem poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee uzn\u225\'e1va cel\u233\'e9 vzdel\u225\'e1vanie \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnych zamestnancov. A preto hovor\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee tento n\u225\'e1vrh je maco\u353\'61sk\u253\'fd vo\u269\'0di u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eom, lebo u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov berie len od roku 2005. Vzdel\u225\'e1vanie, nechce im uzna\u357\'65 to, \u269\'0do mali, a\u382\'7e na prv\u250\'fa a druh\u250\'fa kvalifika\u269\'0dn\u250\'fa sk\u250\'fa\u353\'61ku, to, \u269\'0do mali doteraz uroben\u233\'e9. Opakujem, m\u225\'e1m pocit, \u382\'7ee tento n\u225\'e1vrh v kontexte doby, ktor\u250\'fa \u382\'7eijeme, soci\u225\'e1lnej vl\u225\'e1dy je maco\u353\'61sk\u253\'fd. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pre\u269\'0do? Pre\u269\'0do nevieme uzna\u357\'65 u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eom vzdel\u225\'e1vanie do roku 2005. M\u225\'e1m konkr\u233\'e9tny n\u225\'e1vrh od roku 2002 a nie preto, \u382\'7ee to bola vtedy na\u353\'61a vl\u225\'e1da, ale v roku 2002 sa po\u269\'0d\u237\'edta \u353\'61tat\u250\'fat zamestnanca verejnej slu\u382\'7eby a u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3e je zamestnancom verejnej slu\u382\'7eby. Mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee toto je ten hrani\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd term\u237\'edn, na ktorom by sme sa mohli dohodn\u250\'fa\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee od roku 2002, ke\u271\'0f sa zaviedla verejn\u225\'e1 slu\u382\'7eba, by sme mohli uzna\u357\'65 vzdel\u225\'e1vanie u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov. Pr\u225\'e1ve vtedy potom po zaveden\u237\'ed verejnej slu\u382\'7eby aj enormne nar\u225\'e1stol po\u269\'0det u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov, ktor\u237\'ed prejavili z\u225\'e1ujem sa vzdel\u225\'e1va\u357\'65, aj ke\u271\'0f v podstate za to nemali nejak\u233\'e9 finan\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 benifity.   }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Chcem sa sp\u253\'fdta\u357\'65, pre\u269\'0do je \u250\'fa\u269\'0dinnos\u357\'65 \u167\'a7 53 a \u167\'a7 54, kde sa vych\u225\'e1dza v\~\u250\'fastrety, a je to pozit\u237\'edvne, vych\u225\'e1dza sa v \u250\'fastrety u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eom v tom, \u382\'7ee bud\u250\'fa ma\u357\'65 t\u253\'fd\u382\'7ede\u328\'48 vo\u318\'3ena, \u382\'7ee sa im preplat\u237\'ed polovica n\u225\'e1kladov na lie\u269\'0debn\u253\'fd pobyt. Ale pre\u269\'0do tieto ustanovenia v \u250\'fa\u269\'0dinnosti sa pos\u250\'favaj\u250\'fa do roku 2009, respekt\u237\'edve do roku 2012. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Tento n\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona, ke\u271\'0f hovor\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee je maco\u353\'61sk\u253\'fd, a uviedol som u\u382\'7e minim\u225\'e1lne dva d\u244\'f4vody, a to je to vzdel\u225\'e1vanie a\~ten druh\u253\'fd je posun \u250\'fa\u269\'0dinnosti soci\u225\'e1lnych v\u253\'fdhod, ke\u271\'0f takto m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eem poveda\u357\'65, ale je aj nespravodliv\u253\'fd a maco\u353\'61sk\u253\'fd vo\u269\'0di u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eom, ktor\u237\'ed p\u244\'f4sobia v u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eskej slu\u382\'7ebe viac ako 16 rokov. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Viem, \u382\'7ee protiargumentom m\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee by\u357\'65 to, \u382\'7ee sme uznali prv\u250\'fa a druh\u250\'fa kvalifika\u269\'0dn\u250\'fa sk\u250\'fa\u353\'61ku. A ur\u269\'0dite tento argument je relevantn\u253\'fd, aby tu zaznel, ale ak chceme tento syst\u233\'e9m nastavi\u357\'65 nanovo, som presved\u269\'0den\u253\'fd, \u382\'7ee je nespravodliv\u233\'e9 robi\u357\'65 posuny v tarifn\u253\'fdch triedach o 0,5 % pre u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov, ktor\u237\'ed maj\u250\'fa viac ako 16 rokov praxe a pri t\u253\'fdch za\u269\'0d\u237\'ednaj\u250\'facich o 1 %. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru by sme to mali ma\u357\'65 zjednoten\u233\'e9 a st\u225\'e1le ten posun by mal by\u357\'65 o to 1 %, preto tak ako pri in\u253\'fdch bodoch t\u225\'e1to vl\u225\'e1da by to mala opravi\u357\'65. Na to ste tu, aby ste to opravili, ve\u271\'0f takto to bolo s\u318\'3eubovan\u233\'e9 \u318\'3eu\u271\'0fom. My sme boli t\u237\'ed zl\u237\'ed, prehrali sme vo\u318\'3eby a o\u269\'0dak\u225\'e1vam, p\u225\'e1n minister, \u382\'7ee vy to oprav\u237\'edte, preto sed\u237\'edte na tomto kresle a ja v\u225\'e1m budem len blaho\u382\'7eela\u357\'65, ke\u271\'0f sa v\u225\'e1m to podar\u237\'ed. Zatia\u318\'3e ale nem\u225\'e1te snahu to opravi\u357\'65. (Smiech.)}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u381\'7dia\u318\'3e, v tomto z\u225\'e1kone sa pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru nevyrie\u353\'61i v\u244\'f4bec soci\u225\'e1lny status u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3ea. \u352\'60t\u225\'e1t, ako som povedal, m\u225\'e1 in\u233\'e9 povolania, ktor\u233\'e9 zv\u253\'fdhod\u328\'48uje \u271\'0faleko nad\u353\'61tandardnej\u353\'61ie, ako je povolanie u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov, ak\u233\'e9ko\u318\'3evek deklar\u225\'e1cie o\~tom, ako m\u225\'e1me radi, ako chceme prist\u250\'fapi\u357\'65 k zlep\u353\'61eniu soci\u225\'e1lneho statusu u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov s\u250\'fa len pr\u225\'e1zdnymi heslami a pr\u225\'e1zdnymi gestami, preto\u382\'7ee som uviedol pr\u237\'edklady, ke\u271\'0f mnoh\u233\'e9 in\u233\'e9 profesie s\u250\'fa v pon\u237\'edman\u237\'ed tejto vl\u225\'e1dy hodnoten\u233\'e9, alebo je k nim pristupovan\u233\'e9 omnoho, omnoho materskej\u353\'61ie, ke\u271\'0f nie maco\u353\'61skej\u353\'61ie. Lebo k u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eom sa pristupuje maco\u353\'61sky. Hovor\u237\'edm v\u353\'61ak a opakujem, \u382\'7ee v kontexte prij\u237\'edman\u253\'fdch z\u225\'e1konov. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Som ve\u318\'3emi r\u225\'e1d, \u382\'7ee navrhovate\u318\'3e vysly\u353\'61al aj n\u225\'e1zory opoz\u237\'edcie a vysly\u353\'61al aj n\u225\'e1zory ob\u269\'0dianskych zdru\u382\'7een\u237\'ed, ktor\u253\'fdch nechce pusti\u357\'65 do syst\u233\'e9mu vzdel\u225\'e1vania, a \u382\'7ee sa pochopilo, \u382\'7ee verejn\u253\'fd \u269\'0dinite\u318\'3e nie je to celkom dobr\u233\'e9, \u269\'0do by malo fungova\u357\'65 pri soci\u225\'e1lnom statuse u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3ea. Tresty \u353\'61tyri a\u382\'7e desa\u357\'65 rokov, no, tro\u353\'61ku siln\u225\'e1 k\u225\'e1va. Blaho\u382\'7eel\u225\'e1m ministerstvu, \u382\'7ee to pochopilo a \u382\'7ee uznalo aj pripomienky opoz\u237\'edcie a hovor\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee aj pripomienky ob\u269\'0dianskych zdru\u382\'7een\u237\'ed, \u382\'7ee sme skon\u269\'0dili na pozme\u328\'48uj\u250\'facom n\u225\'e1vrhu, ktor\u253\'fd hovor\u237\'ed o chr\u225\'e1nenej osobe, mysl\u237\'edm. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
N\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona, bohu\u382\'7eia\u318\'3e, v\u244\'f4bec nerie\u353\'61i postavenie odborn\u253\'fdch zamestnancov, aj ke\u271\'0f v jeho n\u225\'e1zve sa to tam u\u382\'7e vs\u250\'fava. V\u244\'f4bec nerie\u353\'61i a nerie\u353\'61i objekt\u237\'edvne a rovnopr\u225\'e1vne v porovnan\u237\'ed s pedagogick\u253\'fdmi zamestnancami postavenie odborn\u253\'fdch zamestnancov centier poradensko-psychologick\u253\'fdch slu\u382\'7eieb, preto\u382\'7ee tam nie je snaha im uzna\u357\'65 ani to\u318\'3eko ko\u318\'3eko u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eom doteraj\u353\'61ie vzdel\u225\'e1vanie a d\u250\'fafam, \u382\'7ee to zmen\u237\'edme. Ja to vytiahnem na osobitn\u233\'e9 hlasovanie aj zo spolo\u269\'0dnej spr\u225\'e1vy, lebo je tam \u269\'0diasto\u269\'0dne ten n\u225\'e1vrh a \u269\'0diasto\u269\'0dne to rie\u353\'61im vo svojom pozme\u328\'48uj\u250\'facom n\u225\'e1vrhu, do \u167\'a7 61. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Ale mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee t\u237\'edto zamestnanci si nezasl\u250\'fa\u382\'7eia, aby boli t\u253\'fdmto z\u225\'e1konom, aj ke\u271\'0f je pravda a ur\u269\'0dite by p\u225\'e1n minister mnoh\u253\'fdm vedel poveda\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee ani my sme to nerie\u353\'61ili, je to pravda. Uzn\u225\'e1vam to a te\u353\'61\u237\'edm sa tomu, \u382\'7ee to rie\u353\'61ite vy. Mysl\u237\'edm si, \u382\'7ee by si t\u237\'edto zamestnanci, odborn\u237\'ed zamestnanci, vzdelan\u237\'ed \u318\'3eudia nezasl\u250\'fa\u382\'7eili, aby boli takto odsunut\u237\'ed t\u253\'fdmto n\u225\'e1vrhom a som r\u225\'e1d, \u382\'7ee p\u225\'e1n minister hovor\u237\'ed, \u382\'7ee sa to bude rie\u353\'61i\u357\'65. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru jedna technick\u225\'e1 pozn\u225\'e1mka je zbyto\u269\'0dn\u225\'e1. To je delenie v \u353\'61kol\u225\'e1ch v\u253\'fdchovn\u253\'fd a kari\u233\'e9rov\u253\'fd poradca. Pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru je to zbyto\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9, a pritom e\u353\'61te v\u253\'fdchovn\u233\'e9mu poradcovi tam ned\u225\'e1vate \u353\'61pecializa\u269\'0dn\u253\'fd pr\u237\'edplatok, pritom ten v\u253\'fdchovn\u253\'fd poradca v podstate rob\u237\'ed ve\u318\'3ek\u250\'fa \u269\'0das\u357\'65 kari\u233\'e9rov\u233\'e9ho poradenstva, ke\u271\'0f pr\u237\'edde, \u269\'0di u\u382\'7e je to \u382\'7eiak z\u225\'e1kladnej \u353\'61koly do deviateho ro\u269\'0dn\u237\'edka, alebo \u382\'7eiak strednej \u353\'61koly do \u353\'61tvrt\u233\'e9ho ro\u269\'0dn\u237\'edka. Pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru ale ned\u225\'e1vam n\u225\'e1vrh k tomu. Pod\u318\'3ea m\u244\'f4jho n\u225\'e1zoru je delenie kari\u233\'e9rov\u253\'fd a v\u253\'fdchovn\u253\'fd poradca zbyto\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 a mohlo by to zosta\u357\'65 na v\u253\'fdchovnom poradcovi. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Za najhor\u353\'61ie alebo za najv\u228\'e4\u269\'0d\u353\'61ie riziko, \u269\'0do je v tomto n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona, v\u353\'61ak pova\u382\'7eujem finan\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 toky. Tento z\u225\'e1kon, prij\u237\'edmaj\u250\'fac v\u353\'61etku kritiku, ktor\u250\'fa my budeme po\u269\'0du\u357\'65 zo strany ministra, tento z\u225\'e1kon prich\u225\'e1dza nesk\u244\'f4r a myslel som, \u382\'7ee aj na minul\u233\'e9 vl\u225\'e1dy. Preto\u382\'7ee tento z\u225\'e1kon prich\u225\'e1dza v \u269\'0dase, ke\u271\'0f nezaznamen\u225\'e1vame ekonomick\u253\'fd a hospod\u225\'e1rsky rast, ale zaznamen\u225\'e1vame pokles hrub\u233\'e9ho dom\u225\'e1ceho produktu a v takomto strmom p\u225\'e1de, \u382\'7ee som niekde \u269\'0d\u237\'edtal, \u382\'7ee ak to dopadne tak, ako to hovor\u237\'ed ministerstvo financi\u237\'ed, tak len na porovnanie, budeme ma\u357\'65 v roku 2009 to\u318\'3eko zdrojov ko\u318\'3eko v roku 2006, ale pripraven\u237\'ed sme na m\u237\'ed\u328\'48anie o 25 % viac, ako bolo pe\u328\'48az\u237\'ed v roku 2006. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Tak\u382\'7ee u\u382\'7e teraz vid\u237\'edm obrovsk\u233\'e9 rizik\u225\'e1 v tom, ako ministerstvo \u353\'61kolstva chce dosta\u357\'65 do syst\u233\'e9mu 31\~442-tis\u237\'edc eur v roku 2010. Ja som d\u225\'e1val pozme\u328\'48uj\u250\'faci n\u225\'e1vrh pri \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tnom rozpo\u269\'0dte zv\u253\'fd\u353\'61i\u357\'65 objem zdrojov ministerstva \u353\'61kolstva o 780 mili\u243\'f3nov kor\u250\'fan a tieto peniaze mali by\u357\'65 pou\u382\'7eit\u233\'e9 na dorovnanie platov zamestnancov \u353\'61kolstva, nie pedagogick\u253\'fdch zamestnancov, ale zamestnancov \u353\'61kolstva na \u250\'farove\u328\'48 priemern\u233\'e9ho platu v n\u225\'e1rodnom hospod\u225\'e1rstve a nepre\u353\'61iel tento n\u225\'e1vrh do rozpo\u269\'0dtu 2009, pritom sme nevedeli o tom, \u382\'7ee bude to, \u269\'0do sa deje teraz, \u382\'7ee bude tak\u253\'fd hlbok\u253\'fd prepad a u\u382\'7e vtedy koal\u237\'edcia odmietla n\u225\'e1vrh na zv\u253\'fd\u353\'61enie, podot\u253\'fdkam o 780 mili\u243\'f3nov. A teraz tu m\u225\'e1me navrhovan\u253\'fdch 950 mili\u243\'f3nov bezm\u225\'e1la. Budem zvedav\u253\'fd, kde to ministerstvo \u353\'61kolstva zoberie. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
E\u353\'61te hor\u353\'61ie na tom s\u250\'fa samospr\u225\'e1vy, preto\u382\'7ee tie maj\u250\'fa tie\u382\'7e probl\u233\'e9my s\u250\'favisiace s v\u253\'fdnosom dane z pr\u237\'edjmu fyzick\u253\'fdch os\u244\'f4b a tam sa o\u269\'0dak\u225\'e1vaj\u250\'fa dopady na ich rozpo\u269\'0dty v roku 2010 780 mili\u243\'f3nov. Rozumiem tomu, pre\u269\'0do ZMOS nechce tento n\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona, preto\u382\'7ee nebude ma\u357\'65 na to peniaze. A preto\u382\'7ee tento z\u225\'e1kon s\u237\'edce bude nap\u237\'edsan\u253\'fd, ale nap\u237\'edsan\u253\'fd tak, \u382\'7ee u\u269\'0ditelia sa maj\u250\'fa pr\u225\'e1vo vzdel\u225\'e1va\u357\'65, ale to ich pr\u225\'e1vo sa nenapln\u237\'ed, preto\u382\'7ee ten riadite\u318\'3e \u353\'61koly od zria\u271\'0fovate\u318\'3ea nebude ma\u357\'65 peniaze za n\u225\'e1klady, aby poslal u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3eov na vzdel\u225\'e1vanie. A tu je kore\u328\'48 probl\u233\'e9mu. \u381\'7de je to nap\u237\'edsan\u233\'e9 slu\u353\'61ne, nie ve\u318\'3emi dobre, ako to chcem  zd\u244\'f4razni\u357\'65, ale v\u353\'61ak slu\u353\'61ne, ale prich\u225\'e1dza to neskoro a nebud\u250\'fa na realiz\u225\'e1ciu tejto normy peniaze. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Chcem sa teda sp\u253\'fdta\u357\'65. Kde bude \u353\'61etri\u357\'65 \u353\'61t\u225\'e1t, kde bude z\u237\'edskava\u357\'65 zdroje ministerstvo \u353\'61kolstva, ako to m\u225\'e1 ministerstvo \u353\'61kolstva dohodnut\u233\'e9 s ministerstvom financi\u237\'ed a ako a kde zober\u250\'fa peniaze obce? Aj napriek kritick\u233\'e9mu t\u243\'f3nu, ako som uviedol, je z\u225\'e1kon posunom vpred, prin\u225\'e1\u353\'61a mnoho dobr\u253\'fdch vec\u237\'ed. A m\u225\'e1m e\u353\'61te jednu ot\u225\'e1zku, a to je, u\u382\'7e to mysl\u237\'edm, \u382\'7ee zaznelo, \u382\'7ee ako teda bude rie\u353\'61en\u233\'e9 vzdel\u225\'e1vanie na odborn\u253\'fdch \u353\'61kol\u225\'e1ch? My sme prijali z\u225\'e1kon o odbornom vzdel\u225\'e1van\u237\'ed. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
A chcem od v\u225\'e1s, p\u225\'e1n minister, relevantn\u250\'fa odpove\u271\'0f, \u269\'0di m\u244\'f4\u382\'7eem do \u353\'61koly zamestna\u357\'65 na ni\u382\'7e\u353\'61\u237\'ed pracovn\u253\'fd \u269\'0das u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3ea \u8211\'13 odborn\u237\'edka z praxe, napr\u237\'edklad na hotelov\u253\'fdch akad\u233\'e9mi\u225\'e1ch, je to u\u269\'0dite\u318\'3e, ktor\u253\'fd m\u225\'e1 ukon\u269\'0den\u233\'e9 vysoko\u353\'61kolsk\u233\'e9 vzdelanie druh\u233\'e9ho stup\u328\'48a na hygienu potrav\u237\'edn a u\u269\'0d\u237\'ed len \u353\'61es\u357\'65 hod\u237\'edn a nepotrebuje ma\u357\'65 ani pedagogick\u233\'e9 minimum, lebo on ho nechce, lebo pracuje \u250\'faplne niekde inde, ale je to odborn\u237\'edk, ktor\u253\'fd zabezpe\u269\'0duje vzdel\u225\'e1vanie na hotelovej akad\u233\'e9mii, \u269\'0di bude m\u244\'f4c\u357\'65 po \u250\'fa\u269\'0dinnosti tohto z\u225\'e1kona p\u244\'f4sobi\u357\'65 v \u353\'61kole? }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Technick\u233\'e9 veci. Na osobitn\u233\'e9 hlasovanie by som vybral body spolo\u269\'0dnej spr\u225\'e1vy. Budem sa sna\u382\'7ei\u357\'65 pomaly \u8211\'13 bod 65, bod 67, bod 68, bod 70, bod 71, 72, 73 a 76 a predt\u253\'fdm e\u353\'61te,  ospravedl\u328\'48ujem sa, bod 31, 36, 50, 59 a 60. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
