Tak\u382\'7ee  navrhujem, aby  v \u167\'a7 12 p\u237\'edsm. f) znelo \u8222\'1e\u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fd tr\u233\'e9ner\u8220\'1c a \u167\'a7 18, aby znel: \u167\'a7 18 \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fd tr\u233\'e9ner. \u8222\'1e\u352\'60kolsk\u253\'fd tr\u233\'e9ner sa pri v\u253\'fdkone pedagogickej \u269\'0dinnosti podie\u318\'3ea na uskuto\u269\'0d\u328\'48ovan\u237\'ed \u353\'61portovej pr\u237\'edpravy ako s\u250\'fa\u269\'0dasti \u353\'61kolsk\u233\'e9ho vzdel\u225\'e1vacieho programu \u353\'61koly.\u8220\'1c }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Od\u244\'f4vodnenie t\u253\'fdchto dvoch paragrafov. P\u244\'f4vodn\u253\'fd n\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona obmedzuje p\u244\'f4sobnos\u357\'65 kateg\u243\'f3rie tr\u233\'e9ner iba pre \u353\'61portov\u233\'e9 \u353\'61koly a \u353\'61portov\u233\'e9 triedy, ale \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fd vzdel\u225\'e1vac\u237\'ed program ktorejko\u318\'3evek \u353\'61koly m\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee vy\u382\'7eadova\u357\'65 p\u244\'f4sobnos\u357\'65 tr\u233\'e9nera aj v tak\u253\'fdch \u353\'61kol\u225\'e1ch alebo triedach, ktor\u233\'e9 nie s\u250\'fa zameran\u233\'e9 na \u353\'61portovo talentovan\u250\'fa ml\u225\'e1de\u382\'7e. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eal\u353\'61\u237\'ed n\u225\'e1vrh. Navrhujem, aby \u167\'a7 20 znel: \u167\'a7 20 psychol\u243\'f3g a \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fd psychol\u243\'f3g. Odsek 2. \u8222\'1e\u352\'60kolsk\u253\'fd psychol\u243\'f3g vykon\u225\'e1va odborn\u233\'e9 \u269\'0dinnosti v r\u225\'e1mci \u353\'61kolsko-psychologickej diagnostiky individu\u225\'e1lneho, skupinov\u233\'e9ho alebo hromadn\u233\'e9ho psychologick\u233\'e9ho poradenstva, psychoterapie, prevencie a intervencie k de\u357\'65om a \u382\'7eiakom s osobitn\u253\'fdm zrete\u318\'3eom na proces v\u253\'fdchovy a vzdel\u225\'e1vania.\u8220\'1c }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Od\u244\'f4vodnenie. P\u244\'f4vodn\u233\'e9 znenie n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona neumo\u382\'7e\u328\'48uje \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fdm psychol\u243\'f3gom vykon\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 diagnostiku v rozsahu ich p\u244\'f4sobnosti, \u269\'0d\u237\'edm by sa de facto znemo\u382\'7enili \u271\'0fal\u353\'61ie \u269\'0dinnosti, ktor\u233\'e9, naopak, pod\u318\'3ea n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona maj\u250\'fa v kompetencii, to znamen\u225\'e1 poradenstvo, psychoterapia, intervencia. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Kolegyne, kolegovia, ak psychol\u243\'f3g nem\u244\'f4\u382\'7ee vykon\u225\'e1va\u357\'65 diagnostiku, ako od neho m\u225\'e1me chcie\u357\'65, aby vykon\u225\'e1val terapiu a vykon\u225\'e1val intervenciu? Pri\u269\'0dom teda  ide o \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fdch psychol\u243\'f3gov, ktor\u253\'fdm toto nie je umo\u382\'7enen\u233\'e9. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
\u270\'0eal\u353\'61\u237\'ed n\u225\'e1vrh. Pozme\u328\'48uj\u250\'faci n\u225\'e1vrh sa t\u253\'fdka \u167\'a7 38. \u167\'a7 38 znie: Funk\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 vzdel\u225\'e1vanie odsek 2. \u8222\'1eFunk\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 vzdel\u225\'e1vanie poskytuje p\u237\'edsmeno d) in\u225\'e1 pr\u225\'e1vnick\u225\'e1 osoba, ktor\u225\'e1 m\u225\'e1 v predmete  \u269\'0dinnosti vzdel\u225\'e1vanie  orientovan\u233\'e9 na mana\u382\'7e\u233\'e9rske sp\u244\'f4sobilosti.\u8220\'1c Od\u244\'f4vodnenie. Obmedzenie poskytovate\u318\'3eov funk\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9ho vzdel\u225\'e1vania iba na organiz\u225\'e1cie  uveden\u233\'e9 v n\u225\'e1vrhu z\u225\'e1kona je v rozpore s cie\u318\'3emi z\u225\'e1kona. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Tak\u382\'7ee to\u318\'3eko pozme\u328\'48uj\u250\'face n\u225\'e1vrhy, ktor\u233\'e9 rie\u353\'61ia na jednej strane to, aby sme umo\u382\'7enili, aby poz\u237\'edcia tr\u233\'e9nera bola nielen v \u353\'61peci\u225\'e1lnych \u353\'61kol\u225\'e1ch orientovan\u253\'fdch na talentovan\u250\'fa ml\u225\'e1de\u382\'7e, ale aj v in\u253\'fdch \u353\'61kol\u225\'e1ch, ve\u271\'0f na to sme prij\u237\'edmali \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fd z\u225\'e1kon, o ktorom sme hovorili, \u382\'7ee chceme necha\u357\'65 slobodu pre \u353\'61koly. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
A na druhej strane je n\u225\'e1vrh, ktor\u253\'fd umo\u382\'7e\u328\'48uje aj \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fdm psychol\u243\'f3gom diagnostikova\u357\'65. Viem, \u382\'7ee s\u250\'fa obavy, \u382\'7ee pri \u353\'61kolsk\u253\'fdch psychol\u243\'f3goch potom by sme mali diagnostikovan\u253\'fdch prive\u318\'3ea det\u237\'ed s r\u244\'f4znymi  sympt\u243\'f3mami. Ale to je u\u382\'7e vec v\u253\'fdkonu tej pr\u225\'e1ce, \u269\'0di t\u225\'e1 diagnostika je, alebo nie je spr\u225\'e1vna. Ka\u382\'7edop\u225\'e1dne bez diagnostiky sa pod\u318\'3ea mojej mienky terapia vykon\u225\'e1va\u357\'65  ned\u225\'e1. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
A na tre\u357\'65om mieste teda navrhujem, aby funk\u269\'0dn\u233\'e9 vzdel\u225\'e1vanie  mohli poskytova\u357\'65 aj in\u233\'e9 organiz\u225\'e1cie, nielen \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tne organiz\u225\'e1cie.  }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
