\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Moja ot\u225\'e1zka vyvst\u225\'e1va z toho, \u382\'7ee t\u237\'ed odborn\u237\'edci sa vyjadrili v tom zmysle, \u382\'7ee pre\u269\'0do nemus\u237\'ed splni\u357\'65 ten svoj cie\u318\'3e, preto\u382\'7ee \u218\'darad pre regul\u225\'e1ciu sie\u357\'65ov\u253\'fdch odvetv\u237\'ed v\u253\'fdnosom z 23. j\u250\'fala 2008 pod \u269\'0d. 6/2008, ktor\u253\'fdm sa ustanovuje regul\u225\'e1cia cien tepla, umo\u382\'7e\u328\'48uje v\u253\'fdrobcovi, dod\u225\'e1vate\u318\'3eovi tepla ur\u269\'0di\u357\'65 z\u225\'e1v\u228\'e4zn\u250\'fa objedn\u225\'e1vku tepla u odberate\u318\'3ea, ktor\u253\'fd rozpo\u269\'0d\u237\'edtava teplo kone\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdm spotrebite\u318\'3eom pod\u318\'3ea spotreby v predch\u225\'e1dzaj\u250\'facom obdob\u237\'ed. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
