\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
P\u225\'e1n minister, v dolo\u382\'7eke finan\u269\'0dn\u253\'fdch ekonomick\u253\'fdch a environment\u225\'e1lnych vplyvov uv\u225\'e1dzate, \u382\'7ee navrhnut\u225\'e1 pr\u225\'e1vna \u250\'faprava nebude ma\u357\'65 dopad na \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tny rozpo\u269\'0det. Je to ve\u318\'3emi jednoduch\u225\'e1 a kr\u225\'e1tka formul\u225\'e1cia. Som presved\u269\'0den\u253\'fd, \u382\'7ee v kone\u269\'0dnom d\u244\'f4sledku za t\u253\'fdch 30 rokov sa tieto cesty splatia zo \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tneho rozpo\u269\'0dtu a z da\u328\'48ov\u253\'fdch poplatn\u237\'edkov. To znamen\u225\'e1, \u382\'7ee bolo by spravodlivej\u353\'61ie uvies\u357\'65, \u382\'7ee v dolo\u382\'7eke environment\u225\'e1lnych vplyvov, \u382\'7ee pre rok 2009 nem\u225\'e1, ale pre \u353\'61t\u225\'e1tny rozpo\u269\'0det a pre ob\u269\'0danov, pre pe\u328\'48a\u382\'7eenky da\u328\'48ov\u253\'fdch poplatn\u237\'edkov tejto krajiny \u225\'e1no. }
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af8\dbch\af11\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f6
Pod\u318\'3ea m\u328\'48a a pod\u318\'3ea viacer\u253\'fdch odborn\u237\'edkov, s ktor\u253\'fdmi som sa stoto\u382\'7enil, by financovanie uveden\u253\'fdch \u250\'fasekov zdrojov Eur\u243\'f3pskej \u250\'fanie bolo najefekt\u237\'edvnej\u353\'61ie a z h\u318\'3eadiska pe\u328\'48a\u382\'7eeniek da\u328\'48ov\u253\'fdch poplatn\u237\'edkov najlep\u353\'61\u237\'edm rie\u353\'61en\u237\'edm. Preto nie som za tak\u233\'e9to r\u253\'fdchle rie\u353\'61enie a nepodpor\u237\'edm tento n\u225\'e1vrh z\u225\'e1kona. \u270\'0eakujem pekne.}
